Integration.RequestFormat:
Market Scout can request research_ops execution via:
{
  "module": "AD_FORENSICS | VISUAL_SCOUT | SOCIAL_MONITOR | ORCHESTRATOR",
  "target": "[URL or search query]",
  "output_format": "[ad_clusters | design_tokens | signal_report | raw_data]",
  "budget": {"max_tool_calls": 20, "max_time_minutes": 10}
}
